  - RULE-PROVIDER,Microsoft,微软服务
  - RULE-PROVIDER,Google,谷歌服务
  - RULE-PROVIDER,Apple,苹果服务
  
  # 国内直连服务
  - RULE-PROVIDER,Lan,DIRECT
  - RULE-PROVIDER,BiliBili,哔哩哔哩
